Our visual workflow designer lets you gain efficiency using automation by creating or modifying rules and process workflows in minutes without writing code. This combination of flexibility and simplicity lets you continuously improve, by easily adapting and evolving your Service Desk or Service Management solution in alignment with your business growth and process maturity.
 
 



 
 
 



Individualized Service Made Simple
 
Our unique Hyper-SaaS™ architecture makes it simple to organize your internal and/or external customers into groups. Each group can have its own automated processes, service catalogs, approvals and dedicated support analysts so you can deliver individualized service and have granular visibility to issues, patterns, trends, and activity.
 
 
 
 




 
 
 



